## Install

```bash
pip install repoclean
```


### Usage

```md
## Usage
```bash
repoclean scan
repoclean init
repoclean fix --dry-run --verbose
repoclean fix --yes
```

## Git Hook (pre-commit)
Install:
repoclean install-hook

Uninstall:
repoclean uninstall-hook
